::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod hears Kluster tell him to get to the CR chamber. He sees that
between the Maximals, and the ship, everything is under control.
"Ok, I will, Kluster." Hot Rod runs in to the Cybertronian Fire, and
gets in a CR chamber.
